name: UFO GO
description:
This is an endless runner game. You are an alien and you have to get to your destination. But the evils robot fishes are interrupting you. So don't hit on them. You can shoot when needed. There are bullets around the space. Collect them!!

Controls:

You can view controls on the game

Made for: Mini-Jam 91

Music from: https://devassets.com/assets/2d-mega-pack/

Software used: Photoshop, Unity 3D
